WebObjects is our application server

00:33:55.500 --> 00:34:01.290
that provides database content for web
services at the back end of a web server.

00:34:01.390 --> 00:34:04.880
It runs on a variety of platforms,
including NTE and Solaris,

00:34:04.880 --> 00:34:06.430
as well as Mac OS X Server.

00:34:06.670 --> 00:34:09.580
