or will be available,

00:35:51.340 --> 00:35:54.570
through Mac OS X Server,
and of course we have them integrated

00:35:54.570 --> 00:35:56.700
with the server offering themselves.

00:35:56.700 --> 00:35:59.790
So that gives you kind of an overview
of where we're going with some of the

00:35:59.790 --> 00:36:01.700
Internet and the file and print services.

